
This is the same demo that was uploaded to wuarchive recently, but
it will now boot properly if extracted straight to disk, and I have
included a complete list of commands.

Enjoy!


AMIGA GUNSHIP 2000 DEMO COMMANDS

-- Simulation Controls --

Quit to Dos		 Q
Pause			 P  (while locked on a target, p will give
                             target info and weapons strategies)
Configuration            C  (while paused)
Easy/Real Flight         F

-- Simulation Views --

Cockpit                 F1              Mast/3D Target View	F2
Left			F3		Right			F4
Chase			F5		Flight Chase		Shift F5
Tactical		F6		Satellite               F7
Reverse Tactical	F8		Missile	                F9
Map View		F10		Change Map Scale    	Space

-- Flight Controls --

Cyclic Forward  	Up 		Cyclic Back		Down
Cyclic Left     	Left		Cyclic Right		Right
Collective Up	        =		Collective Up Fast	Shift =
Collective Down  	-		Coll. Down Fast	        Shift -
Gear Up/Down    	3		Autopilot On/Off	5
Next Waypoint   	6		Previous Waypoint	7
Bay Open/Close  	8		Rotor On/Off		9
Auto Hover		0		

-- Weapon Controls --

Rocket Salvo x1 	1		Rocket Salvo x2	        2
Rocket Salvo x4 	4		Acquire/Next Target	Backspace
Radar Jam On/Off	n		Drop Chaff		m
IR Jam On/Off   	.		Drop Flare		/
Select Weapon   	Space		Fire Weapon		Return


